{"tid":2495443,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"緬甸伊洛瓦底民間武裝組織宣布成立聯邦軍","createTime":"2021-04-19T07:44:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-19T08:24:42.000Z","uid":184679,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ebdac2e9e1121ca559f2d26c08ce1159f45c4e0a","tid":2495443,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T07:44:17.000Z","msg":"來自緬甸伊洛瓦底（Ayeyarwady）、反對軍方發動政變人士4月15日宣布成立伊洛瓦底聯邦軍（Ayeyarwaddy Federal Army，AFA）。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210419/460751053239881728579143.png/9g0N5JrCZetjrpp4FpsT3-D222cP59D2y7PNb8uzzW8?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210419%2F460751053239881728579143.png%2F9g0N5JrCZetjrpp4FpsT3-D222cP59D2y7PNb8uzzW8%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=fc6a7acc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖為伊洛瓦底聯邦軍Facebook帳戶主頁截圖。（Facebook@ayeyarwaddy.federalarmy）<br />\n<br />\n伊洛瓦底聯邦軍當天在Facebook上表示，伊洛瓦底聯邦軍將效忠於聯邦議會代表委員會（CRPH），組建目的包括保護遭迫害人士的生命財產、對抗殘殺無辜平民的「恐怖主義」軍隊、結束軍事獨裁統治並把政權重新移交民選政府手上。<br />\n<br />\n緬甸媒體果敢資訊網18日引述一名革命成員稱，除伊洛瓦底聯邦軍外，另外還有許多革命團體，他們已互相取得聯繫。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210419/460753391665025024320698.jpeg/BOKSuZn439vikaseLXD_Xvc7iuuTbEAfW6SvC1ukrws?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210419%2F460753391665025024320698.jpeg%2FBOKSuZn439vikaseLXD_Xvc7iuuTbEAfW6SvC1ukrws%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=5de19c17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://www.hk01. com/即時國際/613918</code></pre>"},{"pid":"e10c3e389ed3d338b4e4a2b60a5d128bc0c7da5c","tid":2495443,"uid":92836,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T07:45:00.000Z","msg":"香港人十劃都未有四丿"},{"pid":"6598484761b8b2de5fac7e31bda339845d526647","tid":2495443,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e10c3e389ed3d338b4e4a2b60a5d128bc0c7da5c","tid":2495443,"uid":92836,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyT